The paper discusses the optimization of parallel computing systems using meta heuristics and machine learning, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The use of machine learning also suggests the possibility of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) being a relevant sub-category. The paper also discusses software optimization, which falls under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE). The use of meta heuristics suggests the possibility of Programming Languages (cs.PL) being a relevant sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses hardware architecture, which falls under the category of Architecture (cs.AR).
